{"title":"redis安装","uid":"5a4681c603f0c9d9a46ed22467ed2217","slug":"redis安装","date":"2021-10-14T02:35:27.000Z","updated":"2021-10-14T22:51:42.936Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/redis安装.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"redis安装\"><a href=\"#redis安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"redis安装\"></a>redis安装</h1><h2 id=\"1、下载安装包\"><a href=\"#1、下载安装包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、下载安装包\"></a>1、下载安装包</h2><p>官方下载地址：<a href=\"https://redis.io/download\">https://redis.io/download</a></p>\n<p>centos7:下载命令</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;download.redis.io&#x2F;releases&#x2F;redis-6.2.6.tar.gz\ntar xzf redis-6.2.6.tar.gz\ncd redis-6.2.6\nmake<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"2、将redis-server命令加入systemctl服务中\"><a href=\"#2、将redis-server命令加入systemctl服务中\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、将redis-server命令加入systemctl服务中\"></a>2、将redis-server命令加入systemctl服务中</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-shel\" data-language=\"shel\"><code class=\"language-shel\"># 加入systemctl服务文件\nvim &#x2F;lib&#x2F;systemd&#x2F;system&#x2F;redis.service<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">[Unit]\nDescription&#x3D;Redis\nAfter&#x3D;network.target\n\n[Service]\nType&#x3D;forking\nPIDFile&#x3D;&#x2F;var&#x2F;run&#x2F;redis_6379.pid   # 与redis.conf 配置文件中的相应属性保持一致\nExecStart&#x3D;&#x2F;data&#x2F;app&#x2F;redis&#x2F;src&#x2F;redis-server &#x2F;data&#x2F;app&#x2F;redis&#x2F;config&#x2F;redis6379.conf  # 命令的位置和配置文件的位置\nExecReload&#x3D;&#x2F;bin&#x2F;kill -s HUP $MAINPID\nExecStop&#x3D;&#x2F;bin&#x2F;kill -s QUIT $MAINPID\nPrivateTmp&#x3D;true\n[Install]\nWantedBy&#x3D;multi-user.target<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"># 重载系统服务\nsystemctl daemon-reload<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","text":"redis安装1、下载安装包官方下载地址：https://redis.io/download centos7:下载命令 wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;download.redis.io&#x2F;releases&#x2F;redis-6.2.6.tar.gz t...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":817,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据库","slug":"数据库","count":3,"path":"api/categories/数据库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"redis","slug":"redis","count":2,"path":"api/tags/redis.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#redis%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">redis安装</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1、下载安装包</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2%E3%80%81%E5%B0%86redis-server%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5systemctl%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%AD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2、将redis-server命令加入systemctl服务中</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"ChenJinSong","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img.tukuppt.com/ad_preview/00/18/31/5ee60dfa64360.jpg!/fw/980","link":"/","description":"The weak person is dead, and the powerful life.","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"SpringBoot项目发布到外部Tomcat上","uid":"a5da3d0747550d27e33c7318b7278901","slug":"SpringBoot项目发布到外部Tomcat上","date":"2021-10-14T08:25:12.000Z","updated":"2021-10-14T23:03:39.965Z